      <div xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4">
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Hd1e102">III, P. 1, Inq. 1, T. 2, Q. 1, M. 1, C. 4</head>
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Hd1e105" type="question-title">DE LOCUTIONE <mentioned>FACTUM SUB LEGE</mentioned><!--6-->.</head>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e108">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Consequenter quaeritur de hoc quod dicitur:
          <lb ed="#Qd"/><quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e109">Factum sub Lege</quote> etc.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e115">
          <cb ed="#Qd" n="b"/>
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>1. In <title>Psalmo</title> 1, 2 super illum locum: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e120">Et in Lege
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Domini</quote> etc., dicit <name xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Nd1e125">Augustinus</name><!--7-->: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e129">Aliud est<!--q-->
          <pb ed="#Qd" n="99"/>
          <cb ed="#Qd" n="a"/>
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>esse sub lege et aliud<!--a--> in lege. Qui est in lege,
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>secundum legem agit</quote>, voluntarie obediens legi;
          <lb ed="#Qb"/><quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e132">qui autem est sub lege, secundum legem agi<lb ed="#Qd"/>tur</quote>,
          necessitatis timore<!--b--> coactus. Sed in Christo
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>nulla potuit esse coactio.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e140">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>2. Item, <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e160">Iusto non est Lex posita</quote>, <title>I ad Tim.</title> 1<!--c-->, 9;
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>non est igitur Christus sub Lege.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e148">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>3. Item dicit<!--1-->: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e176">Ut redimeret eos qui sub Lege
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>erant</quote>; ergo si ipse erat sub Lege, ipse erat re<lb ed="#Qd"/>dempturus
          se.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e157">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Responsio: 1. Esse sub lege dicitur<!--d--> duobus
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>modis: est enim subiectio voluntaria et est sub<lb ed="#Qd"/>iectio
          necessitatis. Primo modo, secundum pri<lb ed="#Qd"/>mam
          fuit sub lege, sed secundum secundam
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>subiectionem<!--e--> non. Unde <title>Glossa</title><!--2-->, <title>Gal.</title> 4, 5:
          <lb ed="#Qb"/><quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e170"><quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e208">Sub Lege</quote>, id est sub onere Legis, sicut sub
          <cb ed="#Qd" n="b"/>
            <lb ed="#Qd"/>aliis poenis: non ut ab ea expiaretur, sed ut
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>ab ea liberaret</quote>. Unde<!--f--> <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e220">factus sub Lege</quote>, dicit
          <lb ed="#Qd"/><title>Glossa</title><!--3-->: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e181">Ut circumcisus appareat quasi fi<lb ed="#Qd"/>lius
          Abrahae, signum habens eius cui promissus
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>fuerat, in quo impleta est circumcisio, et ita<!--g-->
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>signum iam cessat</quote>.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e191">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>2. Ad illud quod obicitur quod <mentioned>iusto non
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>est Lex posita</mentioned>, dicendum quod hoc dicitur quia
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>quod iustus agit, non agit timore, sed amore:
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Legis autem et Evangelii, sicut dicit <name xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Nd1e251">Augu<lb ed="#Qd"/>stinus</name>,
          <title>Contra Adimantum</title><!--4-->, <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e204">est brevissima<!--h-->
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>differentia, timor et amor</quote>.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-d1e210">
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>3. Ad aliud<!--i--> quod arguit: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e274"><quote xml:id="ahsh-l3p1in1t2q1m1c4-Qd1e275">Ut eos<!--k--> qui sub
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Lege erunt redimeret</quote>, ergo redempturus se</quote>, non
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>sequitur. Nam alio modo dicitur Christus sub
          <lb ed="#Qd"/>Lege, aliter redempturi<!--l--> ab ipso.
        </p>
      </div>
